<MELItem itemNbr="26-22-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-26-22-02.1.2-26-22-02">
<Title>APU Auto Discharge</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided APU fire warning indicator is monitored during APU ground operations.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>During APU ground operations, monitor the APU for fire warnings.  The APU fire extinguisher must be manually discharged using either the APU fire shutdown switch on the P40 service and APU shutdown panel (nose gear) or the APU and Cargo Fire Panel (P5) APU fire switch.</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
